	.col-md-12
		h2 Documentation
		p Created for everyone, everywhere. Is a free and open source forever
		hr
		h3 Quick start
		ul
			li
				b CoderStyle
				| is syntax highlighting project for web developper , very easy to include and integrate in your awesome web application . 
			li
				b Last version :
				| v0.3
			li
				b Languages supported :
				| html , css , bash
			li
				b Templates available : 
				| Monokai , Eiffel , Solarized , Twilight , Github

		h4 Install
		p 
			| Very easy to include in your application , just 
			a(href="#download").tablink download 
			| &nbsp; or clone from github

		.code(cs-lang="bash")
			| $ git clone https://github.com/marwenhlaoui/CoderStyle.git 

		h4 Using
		p
			| You will need to include the style 
			code coderStyle.min.css
			|  and the lib 
			code jquery.min.js
			|  and 
			code coderStyle.min.js
			|  files you downloaded or by cdn in your layout or pages. 
		.code(cs-lang="html")
			|&lt;!DOCTYPE html&gt;
			|&lt;html&gt;
			|	&lt;head&gt;
			|   	...
			| 	<!-- coderstyle css template -->
			| 	&lt;link rel="stylesheet" type="text/css" href="coderStyle.min.css"&gt;
			| 	...
			| 	&lt;/head&gt;
			| &lt;body&gt;
			| 	...
			| 	<!-- JQuery CDN -->
			| 	&lt;script type="text/javascript" src="jquery-3.1.1.min.js"&gt;&lt;/script&gt;
			| 	...
			| 	<!-- coderstyle js -->
			| 	&lt;script type="text/javascript" src="coderStyle.min.js"&gt;&lt;/script&gt;
			| 	...
			|&lt;/body&gt;
			|&lt;/html&gt;
		p
			| Next just call coderstyle function with your 
			code id
			|  or 
			code class
			|  like : 
		.code(cs-lang="html")
			// call with class
			.demo  ... 
			.demo  ... 
			// call with id
			#demo1  ... 
			#demo2  ... 
			script(type='text/javascript').
				$(".demo").coderStyle();
				$("#demo1").coderStyle();
				$("#demo2").coderStyle();
		p
			| You can specify your programming language code with attribut 
			code cs-lang 
			| or in script function by default language : 
		.code(cs-lang="html")
			// language with attr
			.demo(cs-lang='html')  ... 
			// language in function
			script(type='text/javascript').
				$(".demo").coderStyle({
				   "language":"html"
				});
		p
			| You can also specify your template with attribut 
			code cs-theme 
			| or in script function by default theme : 
		.code(cs-lang="html")
			// template with attr
			.demo(cs-theme='monokai')  ... 
			// template in function
			script(type='text/javascript').
				$(".demo").coderStyle({
				   "theme":"monokai"
				});
		p
			| And you can specify your 
			code in-put 
			| or 
			code out-put 
			| code data : 
		.code(cs-lang="html")
			// src of code
			#codeData  ... 
			// show code in 
			#codeShow  ... 
			// script
			script(type='text/javascript').
				$("#codeData").coderStyle({
				   "get":".codeData"
				   "set":".codeShow"
				});

